title: Extortionists (1938, Crime) Daredevil Cameraman, Risks his Life For Front Page Scoop!

sources.title: Extortionists (1938, Crime) Daredevil Cameraman, Risks his Life For Front Page Scoop!
sources.description:
Photographer Flash Casey risks his life to get a front page scoop...gets into a row with the boss, is fired...but makes a hit with the only girl!

Original title: Here's Flash Casey (1938)
Directed by Lynn Shores

Main cast:
Eric Linden - "Flash" Casey
Boots Mallory - Kay Lanning
Cully Richards - Tom Wade
Holmes Herbert - Major Rodney Addison
Joseph Crehan - Blaine (City Editor)
Howard Lang - "Pop" Lawrence
Victor Adams - "King" Ricker
Harry Harvey - Gus Payton
Suzanne Kaaren - Mitzi LaRue
Matty Kemp - Rodney Addison Jr.
Dorothy Vaughan - Mrs.O'Hara (Landlady)
Maynard Holmes - Joe (Roommate)

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/WRXrMJJZUiI
